During the past months I was from time to time reading all kind of stuff related to networking and security. During this process I came accross this book:
{% img http://dl.dornea.nu/img/2015/3b9c034b88c3d5ea44bd4d6bc4436c0f.jpg %}
I found this book to be very comprehensive and very modern in sense of current topics across the &ldquo;network universe&rdquo;. If you ever wanted to get a more deep insight in how routers communicate with each other or how to setup a VoIP infrastructure, this book is a must.
